Package: unacloud

[Groovy] Class LaboratoryController

    • unacloud.LaboratoryController

    • This Controller contains actions to manage laboratory services: crud for laboratory, physical ip and physical machine. This class render pages for user or process request in services to update entities, there is session verification before all actions

      CesarF
